      "text": "- Talk about comic and manga \n   characters I resonate with - Niche\n   is LoreWiki  \n\n-  Talk about current trending \n    topics and tie them into \n    BVC and Caleido-Hope Labs\n\n-  Talk about current events in the \n    Winnipeg Art Community  \n\n-  Sketch things that inspire you in \n   the city \n",
