      "text": " Inter-personal posts \n\n1. Current Events happeaning in the \n   Winnipeg and Zimbabwean Art \n   Communities \n\n2. Talk about Ages of Humanity \n\n3.  Talk about long form content made \n     on youtube around DC, Marvel or \n     manga characters \n\n4. Sketch things that inspire you in the \n   city from day to day \n\n5. Talk about working on BVC through \n    Caleido-Hope Labs \n\n6. Talk about the current books we are \n    printing ",
